                    </div>

                    <p class="status small" data-default="Drop image to the textarea! ðŸ––" data-uploading="Uploading file. Be patient! ðŸ™„" data-uploaded="File has been uploaded! ðŸŽ‰" data-error="File upload failed! ðŸ˜¢">Drop image to the textarea! ðŸ––</p>
